The Lagos chapter of Nigerian Institute of Public Relations is set to hold a Public Relations (PR) clinic for professionals and practitioners. The event tagged ‘Lagos PR Clinic 59th Independence Edition’ will be centred on the topic, ‘’Culture as PR, Perspectives for the Profession and Practice.’’ The PR Clinic hosted by the managing director of Philosoville Limited, Mr Kufre Ekanem will take place on Thursday 3rd October 2019 by 3pm at Elomaz Hotel, 3/5 Immanuel Street, by Mobil station, Maryland, Ikeja, Lagos, Nigeria. Entry to the event is free.